name: Stripes Galore (Hard Cover)
description:
Our Stripes Galore Cover are horizontal stripes that fade into a spectrum of shades of gray gifted wrapped in a bow available in quartet of custom colors; Signature Red, Golden Rod Yellow, Royal Purple and Vibrant Teal Blue. Lastly, each calendar is topped with our exclusive logo. 

Our Calendars are custom designed to accommodate the needs of the Cosmetologist's, Beautician's and Hair Magician's. Each calendar is printed on 8.5X11 paper to offer hourly planning for the traditional cosmetology work week, Tuesday through Saturday with block planning for Sunday and Monday. Also, our standard calendars are designed with 1/2 hour blocks that starts from 8:00am and end at 7:30pm. Please email us at info@cosmocalendar.com if you would like to customize the times for your calendar.  

Please note: 

10% of the proceeds from each Cosmetologist's Calendar sold will go towards the The Chantel Quarles Continuing Education Scholarship Fund and the Ayana Simmons Scholarship Fund. Please visit our website at www.cosmocalendar.com for the specific details for each scholarship fund.

All our calendars are PRE-ORDERED please allow 2-3 weeks for custom processing, unless otherwise specified.

name: Client/Distributor Information Address Book
description:
Our Client/Distributor Information Address Book is available in ONLY Hard Cover. It was designed just in case you lose your phone or drop it in the sink while washing someone's hair and can no longer access your contact list. This is a one stop reference manuals about the individuals that you provide  serve and the people that help your business run smoothly, your distributors. This calendar is available in any of the calendar covers featured on out website. 

This book encompasses pertinent contact information for your clients and distributers, as well as, extra space for notes you may need to keep about each individual. 

Our Client/Distributor Information Address Book are custom designed to accommodate the needs of the Cosmetologist's, Beautician's and Hair Magician's. Each address book is printed on 8.5X11 paper. Each letter of the alphabet offers 18 entries for Client Information. Additionally, there are 10 entries for vendor information for the Distributors Lists.

Please email us at info@cosmocalendar.com if you would like to customize your address book.
